data.title: Software Engineering Associate
bullets: Collaborated closely with SSMHealth to debug and resolve issues on their Kentico CMS based website in C# with .NET MVC.
Implemented and deployed over 30 features to production environments for companies through writing optimal and maintainable code. Primarily worked with C# in the .NET MVC web application framework.
Engaged in an end-to-end agile software development cycle, leveraging Azure DevOps CI/CD pipelines and unit testing within a collaborative team environment

data.title: Cashier/Bagger
bullets: Demonstrated exceptional communication skills by interacting with more than 100 customers daily.
Surpassed performance standards and received 2 documented compliments from customers for delivering excellent service.
